lead_paragraph: Formula One's governing body got it wrong twice over with Ferrari's Sebastian Vettel at last weekend's Mexican Grand Prix, according to former race winner and television pundit Johnny Herbert.

headline.print_headline: FIA Wrong on Two Counts With Vettel, Says Herbert
